sample_treatment_protocol_ch1: Nuclei were isolated from fresh-frozen post-mortem human caudate nucleus and putamen, labeled with cell type-specific probes and separated by FACS as described by Matlik et al. 2023.
sample_extract_protocol_ch1: RNA extraction was carried out with AllPrep DNA/RNA FFPE Kit (Qiagen, #80234)., RNA-seq libraries were prepared with Trio RNA-Seq™ library preparation kit (Tecan, #0506-A01) and pooled for sequencing on NovaSeq6000 (SP 2 x 150bp).
sample_description: 3357, RNA extracted from DRD1-expressing striatal projection neuron nuclei (PPP1R1B+, DRD1+, DRD2-)
sample_data_processing: Sequence and transcript coordinates for human hg38 UCSC genome and gene models were retrieved from the BSgenome.Hsapiens.UCSC.hg38 Bioconductor package (version 1.4.1) and TxDb.Haspiens.UCSC.hg38.knownGene (version 3.4.0) Bioconductor libraries respectively. FANSseq reads were aligned to the genome using Rsubread's subjunc method (version 1.30.6)., Aligned reads were exported as bigWigs normalized to reads per million using the rtracklayer package (version 1.40.6)., Aligned reads in genes were c ...

sample_extract_protocol_ch1: RNA extraction was carried out with AllPrep DNA/RNA FFPE Kit (Qiagen, #80234)., RNA-seq libraries were prepared with Trio RNA-Seq™ library preparation kit (Tecan, #0506-A01) and pooled for sequencing on NovaSeq6000 (SP 2 x 150bp).

sample_description: 4868, RNA extracted from oligodendrocyte nuclei (OLIG2+, EAAT1-, NeuN-, IRF8-)
sample_data_processing: Sequence and transcript coordinates for human hg38 UCSC genome and gene models were retrieved from the BSgenome.Hsapiens.UCSC.hg38 Bioconductor package (version 1.4.1) and TxDb.Haspiens.UCSC.hg38.knownGene (version 3.4.0) Bioconductor libraries respectively. FANSseq reads were aligned to the genome using Rsubread's subjunc method (version 1.30.6)., Aligned reads were exported as bigWigs normalized to reads per million using the rtracklayer package (version 1.40.6)., Aligned reads in genes were c ...

sample_source_name_ch1: gDNA extracted from striatal astrocyte nuclei (EAAT1+, IRF8-, NeuN-, OLIG2-) treated with Tn5 transposase
sample_treatment_protocol_ch1: Nuclei were isolated from fresh-frozen post-mortem human caudate nucleus and putamen, treated with Tagment DNA TDE1 Enzyme (Illumina, #15027865), labeled with cell type-specific probes and separated by FACS as described by Matlik et al 2023.
sample_extract_protocol_ch1: Genomic DNA was isolated with using MinElute Reaction Cleanup Kit (Qiagen, #28206), Genomic DNA was used for PCR amplification with NEBNext® High-Fidelity 2X PCR Master Mix (New England Biolabs, #M0541S) and barcoded Nextera primers (Buenrostro JD et al., 2013, Nat Methods 10, 1213-1218. 10.1038/nmeth.2688). Libraries were pooled for sequencing on NovaSeq6000 (SP 2 x 150bp or SP 2 x 100bp).
sample_data_processing: The ATACseq reads were aligned with the hg38 genome from the BSgenome.Hsapiens.UCSC.hg38 Bioconductor package (version 1.4.1) using Rsubread's align method in paired-end mode., Normalized bigWigs were created with the rtracklayer package., BSgenome.Hsapiens.UCSC.hg38

Libraries were pooled for sequencing on NovaSeq6000 (SP 2 x 150bp or SP 2 x 100bp).
sample_data_processing: The ATACseq reads were aligned with the hg38 genome from the BSgenome.Hsapiens.UCSC.hg38 Bioconductor package (version 1.4.1) using Rsubread's align method in paired-end mode., Normalized bigWigs were created with the rtracklayer package., BSgenome.Hsapiens.UCSC.hg38
